{
  "texts": [
    "• LMSYS-Chat-1M (Zheng et al, 2023a).",
    "The LMSYS-Chat-1M dataset comprises 1M instances of authentic dialogue data, collected from various models responding to questions on a website.",
    "To ensure the secure release of the data, the creators remove conversations containing personal identifying information.",
    "However, they retain unsafe dialogues for the purpose of studying robustness and security.",
    "• MOSS 002 sft data (Sun et al, 2023b)."
  ]
}